OL,3,COut-of-date government IT systems
OL,4,C'hampering public sector adoption of
OL,5,CAI'
OL,7,FOut-of-date technology and poor
OL,8,Fquality data are putting the
OL,9,FGovernment's plans to scale up the
OL,10,Fadoption of artificial intelligence
OL,11,F(AI) in the public sector at risk, a
OL,12,Freport from MPs says.
OL,14,FIn its analysis of the Government's
OL,15,Fuse of AI, the Public Accounts
OL,16,FCommittee said that while the
OL,17,Ftechnology had the potential to
OL,18,Fradically change public services, the
OL,19,Fscale of the task to grasp these
OL,20,Fopportunities was concerning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
