OL,3,COut-of-date government IT systems
OL,4,C'hampering public sector adoption of
OL,5,CAI'
OL,7,FEarlier this year, the Prime Minister
OL,8,Funveiled a major plan to make the UK
OL,9,Fan AI "superpower" by investing
OL,10,Fheavily in the technology and its
OL,11,Fsurrounding infrastructure in order to
OL,12,Fmake it a hub for investment, but also
OL,13,Fby increasing AI adoption in Whitehall
OL,14,Fand the wider public sector to help
OL,15,Fcut costs and waste, as well as
OL,16,Fimprove productivity.
