OL,3,COut-of-date government IT systems
OL,4,C'hampering public sector adoption of
OL,5,CAI'
OL,7,FThe committee's report said an
OL,8,Festimated 28% of central government IT
OL,9,Fsystems in 2024 could be defined as
OL,10,Fout of date and impossible to update,
OL,11,Fand that a third of the 72 highest-
OL,12,Frisk legacy systems lacked the
OL,13,Fremediation funding to fix the problem.
OL,15,FIt also said government data was too
OL,16,Foften of poor quality and as a result
OL,17,Fwas putting efficient AI adoption at
OL,18,Frisk because the technology relies on
OL,19,Fand requires high quality data in
OL,20,Forder to learn.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
