OL,3,COut-of-date government IT systems
OL,4,C'hampering public sector adoption of
OL,5,CAI'
OL,7,FIn addition, the committee warned that
OL,8,Fpublic trust in AI was being
OL,9,Fjeopardised by slow progress from
OL,10,Fgovernment in being transparent about
OL,11,Fwhen and how the technology is being
OL,12,Fused in public sector decision making,
OL,13,Fand that a general lack of digital
OL,14,Fskills across the public sector was a
OL,15,Fbarrier to AI adoption.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
