OL,7,FAccording to figures in the report, as
OL,8,Fof January this year only 33 records
OL,9,Fhave been published on the government
OL,10,Fwebsite set up to provide transparency
OL,11,Fon how AI had been used in decision
OL,12,Fmaking.
OL,14,FThe report included a number of
OL,15,Frecommendations for the Department for
OL,16,FScience, Innovation and Technology
OL,17,F(DSIT), including prioritising funding
OL,18,Fto ensure that IT systems were brought
OL,19,Fup to date.
