OL,7,FSir Geoffrey Clifton-Brown, chairman
OL,8,Fof the Public Accounts Committee,
OL,9,Fsaid: "This committee's role is to
OL,10,Fhelp ensure efficient Government
OL,11,Fpolicy delivery through our
OL,12,Frecommendations.
OL,14,F"The potential for AI to secure
OL,15,Fwidespread efficiencies is obvious,
OL,16,Fand the need for digital improvements
OL,17,Fis a theme that will run through all
OL,18,Four inquiries as through a stick of
OL,19,Frock.
