OL,7,F"The AI industry needs a Government
OL,8,Fthat is on its side, while making sure
OL,9,Fthat any opportunities for improvement
OL,10,Fare seized in a safe and ethical way.
OL,12,F"Transparency is key here, as public
OL,13,Ftrust that AI will work for them is
OL,14,Fcentral to any successful use of it.
OL,16,F"We still have a long way to go in
OL,17,Fthis area.
