OL,7,F"The Government has said it wants to
OL,8,Fmainline AI into the veins of the
OL,9,Fnation, but our report raises
OL,10,Fquestions over whether the public
OL,11,Fsector is ready for such a procedure.
OL,13,F"The ambition to harness the potential
OL,14,Fof one of the most significant
OL,15,Ftechnological developments of modern
OL,16,Ftimes is of course to be welcomed.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
