OL,3,COut-of-date government IT systems
OL,4,C'hampering public sector adoption of
OL,5,CAI'
OL,7,F"Unfortunately, those familiar with
OL,8,Four committee's past scrutiny of the
OL,9,FGovernment's frankly sclerotic digital
OL,10,Farchitecture will know that any
OL,11,Fpromises of sudden transformation are
OL,12,Ffor the birds.
OL,14,F"A transformation of thinking in
OL,15,FGovernment at senior levels is
OL,16,Frequired, and the best way for this to
OL,17,Fhappen is for digital professionals to
OL,18,Fbe brought round the top table in
OL,19,Fmanagement and governing boards of
OL,20,Fevery department and their agencies.
