OL,7,F"I have serious concerns that DSIT
OL,8,Fdoes not have the authority over the
OL,9,Frest of Government to bring about the
OL,10,Fscale and pace of change that's needed.
OL,12,F"We hope the recommendations in our
OL,13,Freport aid the Government in
OL,14,Fsucceeding in bringing public sector
OL,15,Fsystems into the 21st century for
OL,16,Ftheir users, where other efforts have
OL,17,Ffailed."
